title: A Date with Python: Freshman Inter-section Programming Competition
description: February 14, 2024 - Mapúa MCL-ACM hosted its second annual 'A Date with Python,' where IT101-2L students coded their way to a romantic dinner. Running from 10:45 AM to 2:30 PM, the event mixed the thrill of a coding competition with Valentine's Day festivities. Shamelle Climaco and Sophia Narcelles from Team Siomai of Section B52 emerged as the champions, winning a free date. The event was marked by enthusiastic participation and strong camaraderie, solidifying its place as a cherished tradition at Mapúa MCL-ACM.
summary: On February 14, Mapúa MCL-ACM hosted its second annual 'A Date with Python,' where IT101-2L students coded their way to a romantic dinner.
